Selections include such obvious choices as "&#039;Round Midnight" (Scott Hamilton) and "In the Wee Small Hours of the Morning" (Carol Sloane), plus tracks by Concord Jazz recording artists Mel Torm?, Marian McPartland, Gene Harris, and many more.
